                        <li>
                           <a href="$app/departmenthistory/people/secretaries">Biographies</a>
                                of the Secretaries of State and suggestions for further reading
                                about these public servants;</li>
                        <li>Extensive lists of the past <a href="$app/departmenthistory/people/principals-chiefs">Principal
                                    Officers of the Department of State and Chiefs of Mission</a>
                                organized by position, country, and name; </li>
